OL,3,CBaby survives after being born at just
OL,4,C22 weeks old
OL,6,FA baby has survived after being born
OL,7,Fat just 22 weeks old.
OL,9,FIsaac has become the youngest newborn
OL,10,Fat Coventry's University Hospital to
OL,11,Fmake it back home with his parents.
OL,13,FHe was born extremely prematurely in
OL,14,FFebruary, weighing about 1.2lbs -
OL,15,Froughly the same as a large block of
OL,16,Fbutter.
OL,18,FHe was then cared for at the neonatal
OL,19,Funit, and made remarkable progress. He
OL,20,Fnow weighs almost 6lbs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
