PN,34502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784575122
OL,3,CBaby survives after being born at just
OL,4,C22 weeks old
OL,6,FHe has been taken home for the first
OL,7,Ftime by his parents, mother Vimbay and
OL,8,Ffather Tatenda, where his two siblings
OL,9,Fwelcomed him.
OL,11,FVimbay said: "It was one of the
OL,12,Fscariest moments of my life and it has
OL,13,Fbeen an emotional rollercoaster. We've
OL,14,Fcelebrated every gram he has gained!
OL,16,F"There have been moments of fear and
OL,17,Fmoments of exhaustion, but there have
OL,18,Falso been moments of hope, and my
OL,19,Ffaith has carried me through this.
OL,26,@sD@NOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784575122
OL,3,CBaby survives after being born at just
OL,4,C22 weeks old
OL,6,F"The nursing team and neonatal staff
OL,7,Fhave been amazing. Isaac wouldn't have
OL,8,Fgot to where he is now without them.
OL,10,F"When he was in intensive care, that
OL,11,Fwas the hardest time, and the nurses
OL,12,Fthere have such a big job caring for
OL,13,Fthe tiniest children.
OL,15,F"At first I just wanted to go home
OL,16,Fwith my baby, but then the thought of
OL,17,Fgoing home was scarier than staying in
OL,18,Fhospital. I'm receiving a lot of
OL,19,Fsupport from the Neonatal Community
OL,20,FOutreach Team and that is really
OL,21,Freassuring."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
