OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784575122
OL,3,CBaby survives after being born at just
OL,4,C22 weeks old
OL,6,FApproximately seven in 10 babies born
OL,7,Fat 22 weeks do not survive labour or
OL,8,Fthe immediate post-natal period.
OL,10,FTracey Brigstock, Chief Nursing
OL,11,FOfficer at University Hospitals
OL,12,FCoventry and Warwickshire NHS Trust,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Isaac's journey is a powerful
OL,14,Fexample of the strength shown by
OL,15,Fbabies, families and staff every day
OL,16,Fin our Neonatal services.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
